### DESCRIPTION
### Makes Iron Bear/Iron Cub deal no self-damage, so it can have even a chance to use
### its splash weapons, especially at higher mayhem levels. I don't know why this 
### isn't how it works by default.
### 


###
### MINIGUN
###

## Exploding Bullets (Augment 3)
# Projectiles deal no self-damage 
SparkLevelPatchEntry,(1,1,0,MatchAll),/Game/PlayerCharacters/Gunner/_Shared/_Design/IronBear/HardPoints/Minigun/DamageData/DamageData_Minigun_ExplodingBullets.Default__DamageData_Minigun_ExplodingBullets_C,bCanHurtInstigator,0,,false
SparkLevelPatchEntry,(1,1,0,MatchAll),/Game/PlayerCharacters/Gunner/_Shared/_Design/IronBear/HardPoints/Minigun/DamageData/DamageData_Minigun_ExplodingBullets.Default__DamageData_Minigun_ExplodingBullets_C,bCanHurtSelf,0,,false


